title: Kilmarnock 1-0 Rangers: Who impressed?
title_page: Kilmarnock 1-0 Rangers: Who impressed? - BBC Sport
maintext:
You could make the case for plenty in blue and white stripes, but Danny Armstrong epitomised Kilmarnock's display in their opening-day win over Rangers.
Last term's talisman was relentless with his energy on the right in both defence and attack.
